title: Pete Prisco on Revis retiring, Cooks extension, Jaguars legit Super Bowl chances (Football 07/19)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Pete Prisco to break down the latest news around the NFL, including the retirement of Darrelle Revis, Brandin Cooks' extension from the Rams and what it means for Aaron Donald, Cardinals GM Steve Keim getting suspended for five weeks, what Le'Veon Bell could get on the open market, Terrell Owens Hall of Fame controversy and Malik Jackson saying the Jaguars can go 16-0. The guys then dive into just how good Jacksonville can be in 2018 and how the rest of the AFC looks plus much more.
